    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "6. spake I a word to any of the judges—In 2Sa 7:7 it is \"any of the tribes\" of Israel. Both are included. But the judges \"who were commanded to feed the people,\" form the more suitable antithesis to David.",
        "children": []
